caption.1: Were betting on @kennethbrother and when you listen to his tracks, youll know why. He took his love for football all the way to the college level, before becoming one of New Orleans top up-and-coming hip-hop artists. Check him out in our playlist yall, link in bio. #BetOnNOLA
caption.2: We#BetOnNOLAand@sleazyezdoes too. Born and raised in New Orleans, her music is influenced by the citys resilience, as well as her love for New Orleans street culture. Her goal is to represent all women and the Black LGBTQ+ community through her music, and give them the chance to impact the world in their own way. Check out her tracks in our playlist in the bio.
